        {
            "title": "美國債息向下  10 年期國債息率四連跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國國債息周五下跌，美債錄得自美伊戰爭爆發以來最佳一周表現。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美國國債。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美國國債。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美國國債。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國10年期國債收益率下行1.4個基點至4.441厘，已連續4交易日下行，一度回升1.38個基點，至4.461厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2年期收益率下跌2.9個基點至3.996厘，一度降3.7個基點，至3.988厘。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本周債券價格向上，債息向下，與月初債券因戰爭通脹擔憂而大幅拋售形成鮮明反轉，停火談判進展是這一轉變的直接驅動力，聯儲局副主席(Michelle Bowman發表演說，稱現時判斷伊朗戰爭對通脹的影響言之過早。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16085618-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%90%91%e4%b8%8b-10-%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%e5%9c%8b%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e7%8e%87%e5%9b%9b%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190902_FI_US-TREASURY-BONDS_US-BOND_FB-1-2-1-1-1-1_source-web_-1-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-30 12:45:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "ADR高水66點  美團滙控向好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR較恆指周五收市高66點或0.26%，報25248點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)成主力，ADR折合港元計收報77.08元，較香港收市價升4.9%，貢獻恒指31點 ; 藥明生物(02269)ADR折合港元計收報77.08元，較香港收市價升2% ; 百度(09888)ADR折合港元計收報132.55元，較香港收市價升2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報146.93元，較香港收市價升1.3%，貢獻恒指27點 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣134.36元，較香港收市價0.3%，貢獻恒指12點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR折合港元計收報427.91元，較香港收市價0.2% ; 攜程(09961)ADR收市折合港幣371.71元，較香港收市價高0.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">理想汽車(02105)反彈，ADR收市折合港幣58.82元，較香港收市價高1.7% ; 比亞迪(01211)ADR收市折合港幣90.83元，較香港收市價低0.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報25098點，升109點，較昨日恒指收市25182點，低水84點，成交15312張。國指夜市期指收報8398點，較昨日國指收市低水28點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16085444-adr%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b466%e9%bb%9e-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%98%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-30 12:05:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價低收近2%　憧憬美伊達成協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價下跌，市場預期美伊最終可望就延長停火達成協議，緩和供應緊張憂慮。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/79d4fe226494eb79aca6b4bb92e5c6a0_Election_2_26_New_Mexico_Oil_Windfall_498_2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/79d4fe226494eb79aca6b4bb92e5c6a0_Election_2_26_New_Mexico_Oil_Windfall_498_2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7月紐約期油收報每桶87.36美元，下跌1.54美元，跌幅1.73% ; 7月倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶92.05美元，下跌1.66美元，跌幅1.77%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">總結本月表現，布蘭特期油累計下跌逾19%；紐約期油則跌近17%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16084690-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e8%bf%912%e3%80%80%e6%86%a7%e6%86%ac%e7%be%8e%e4%bc%8a%e9%81%94%e6%88%90%e5%8d%94%e8%ad%b0",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/OIL-PRICE_FB_source-ap_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-30 11:23:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股破頂道指升穿5萬關　戴爾升逾三成  本月升近3%至8%以上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股3大指數連續3日創收市新高，道瓊斯工業平均指數更首次升穿51000點關口，戴爾（Dell）急升近33%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Dell 。 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/d8f268c0229d42069f316d7b09ba6172_Dell_Pro_5_Micro.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Dell 。 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/d8f268c0229d42069f316d7b09ba6172_Dell_Pro_5_Micro.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Dell 。 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股受惠人工智能熱潮持續發酵，加上市場憧憬美伊有望達成進一步停火協議，美股全星期及全月均錄得顯著升幅。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>三大指數齊創收市新高</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">道瓊斯指數收報51032點，升363點，升幅0.72%。高開104點後，升幅擴大至最多425點，最高報51094點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">納斯達克指數收報26972點，升55點，升幅0.2%，一度上揚0.66%至27094點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">標準普爾500指數收報7580點，升16點，升幅0.22%。標指曾漲0.47%至7599點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">個股方面，戴爾（Dell）股價急升32.8%，成為市場焦點。公司上調全年盈利預測，大幅提振投資者信心。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IBM炒高12.7%，為升幅最大道指成份股。大型科技股則個別發展，微軟（Microsoft）升5.45%，表現強勢；Meta則偏軟，跌0.44%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>標指連升9星期創逾一年最長升市</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">回顧全周表現，道指累計上升0.9%，納指升2.4%，標普500指數升1.43%。值得留意的是，標指已連升9個星期，是2023年12月以來最長升市，反映市場動力持續強勁。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>5月納指跑贏累升8.4%</strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">總結5月份，納指表現最為突出，累計升幅達8.4%；標普500指數升5.2%；道指則升2.8%。人工智能熱潮帶動科技股成為本月升市火車頭，推動大市反覆向上。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16084686-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e7%a0%b4%e9%a0%82%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf5%e8%90%ac%e9%97%9c%e3%80%80%e6%88%b4%e7%88%be%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be%e4%b8%89%e6%88%90-%e6%9c%ac%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%913",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20200617_FI_US-STOCK_FB-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1_source-ap_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-30 10:58:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股收市持平   國防股升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲3大指數收市變動不大，泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市彈0.14%，報626點，最多曾漲0.69%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國富時100指數收報10409點，跌16點或0.16%；法國CAC指數收報8183點，跌5點或0.07%；德國DAX指數收報25104點，升12點或0.05%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利富時MIB指數收報50036點，進賬0.42%或211點；西班牙IBEX 35指數收報18362點，上揚0.46%或83點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">俄羅斯無人機擊中羅馬尼亞一座公寓大樓，消息刺激歐洲航空航太與國防指數上漲逾2%，波蘭航空航太與微型衞星公司Creotech股價上漲4%；奧地利航空航太公司FACC攀升4.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16084675-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e6%8c%81%e5%b9%b3-%e5%9c%8b%e9%98%b2%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87",
